{{#content "post-content"}}
<h2>On the first day of Christmas&hellip;</h2>
<p>As this project is a bit of fun and I’ve been doing it in a bit of spare time, I thought it was a good chance to use some funky new progressive CSS3 techniques to bring the calendar to life.</p>
